<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Quote Rejected - Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .details {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .info-badge {
            background: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .price-highlight {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸ“‹ Quote Update</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= Recipient %>,</h2>

            <div class="info-badge">
                <strong>Your quote was not accepted this time</strong>
            </div>

            <p>We wanted to let you know that the buyer <strong>
                    <%= BuyerName %>
                </strong> has decided not to proceed with your quote for this order.</p>

            <div class="details">
                <h3>ðŸ“‹ Quote Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Truck ID:</strong>
                    <%= TruckId %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Loading Depot:</strong>
                    <%= LoadingDepot %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Destination:</strong>
                    <%= Destination %>, <%= City %>, <%= State %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Expected Arrival:</strong>
                    <%= TruckArrivalTime %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Decision Time:</strong>
                    <%= OrderTime %>
                </p>

                <div class="price-highlight">
                    <h3>ðŸ’° Your Quote Price: <%= QuotePrice %>
                    </h3>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Don't worry!</strong> This happens in business, and there are always more opportunities.</p>

            <p><strong>What you can do:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Review your pricing strategy and resend another quote</li>
                <li>Check market rates in your area</li>
                <li>Look for other available orders on the platform</li>
                <li>Continue building your reputation with successful deliveries</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= OrderUrl %>" class="button">Browse Available Orders</a>
            </div>

            <p>Keep up the great work, and thank you for being part of the FuelsGate community!</p>

            <!-- <p>Best regards,<br>
                <strong>FuelsGate Team</strong>
            </p> -->
        </div>

        <%- include("./shared/footer") %>

    </div>
</body>

</html>